> I'm using hwclock which comes with the util-linux-2.9i package.
Could you try upgrading to some more recent util-linux
like 2.9x? (Roughly speaking not very much has changed in util-linux,
but hwclock was completely rewritten.)
I do not recall seeing a problem with the new hwclock that was not
fixed by giving it --directisa.
